	(text_box "H755 control board features\n\n5 HRTIM complementary channels\n3 TIM1 complementary channels\n3 optional TIM8 complementary channels\n14 ADC inputs (4 ADC1, 3 ADC2, 7 ADC3)\n4 dedicated GPIO\n4 testpoints (supply, GND, interrupt pin)\n1 I2C\n2 SPI\n1 CANFD\n1 UART\n\n\nBoard features\nSix layers\nSTLink 14 pin connector\n1A 3V3 LDO output\n5 V input (optional 2pin header for debug)\nparallel diode reverse protection\n1.5mm Castellation pitch\nRJ45 100Mbit/s Ethernet\n"
